name: 8min Rolling TT
description:
Today's session consists of 2 x 8 minute rolling TT intervals. Rolling intervals are performed within Zone 4. However, each 8-minute interval is preceded by a 30 second Zone 5 effort. 



However, today aims to disrupt your rhythm by moving the target power up and down every minute.
